reviews.text: This is probably the worst McDonald's in Hong Kong - guaranteed food is never made to order and stored for hours under the heat lamp,  hence poor quality expected! Fries are made in advance and when you want fresh fries the staff frown at you! But then again, you're lucky if you don't get cursed at! First McDonald's ever to see the staff swear at customers and ask about their mother 🙄, for not queuing properly. No sense of service with a smile or to have quality food. The 'bin' level of burgers is so much .. Even when it's not busy. This is not managed properly - not hygienic!
You get fast food here. You can get an excellent price/performance for ice-cream cone. It is consistently in food favors no matter which Mac you go.
Nice location but a little too busy!
No surprise in food & a bit disappointed in queuing up for meal over 15 mins
The place is usually crowded with families and the queues can get very long in the late afternoons.  The exteriors are a bit rundown and the canopy is precariously worn out.

reviews.text: It was very delicious. When I pass this store,always there were lot's of people waited to get foods. Today I finally try chicken rice and it was awesome.
Delicious and affordable. Only small amount of chicken per portion though.

They always serve the best chicken around this area. However, they increase the price and decrease the chicken portion. Their portion is still huge because they give you a lot of rice! So they can use less chicken. I don’t mind to pay for this price, but I hope I can get more chicken.

Delicious Hainan Chicken served here!  Chicken is cooked just right, very tender and juicy.  The rice is filled with flavor after being cooked with chicken fat.  The sauces perfectly compliments the flavor of the chicken and rice.  

The best food stall within Tai On Building.  This is the perfect choice for a cheap lunch!
Delicious yet inexpensive.

result.name: 海南雞專門店(第二分店)

reviews.text: 位處於太安樓第二街,有一小撮可以坐低食嘢嘅地方.但係因為地方淺窄,又超多人排隊.你總會覺得有點兒擠迫,尤其是其他鋪頭送貨甚至大廈倒垃圾等等有大型的輪子手推車經過的時候,你就會覺得很是討厭但又做唔到啲乜嘢... 因為百物騰貴,已經加咗好幾次價 假如三五知己去呢度食嘅話,我建議你買半隻/一隻雞,再加油飯白飯食:因為嗌碟頭飯,得嗰幾件雞.食極唔飽,計起嚟價錢亦都比較貴.上次我跟我阿姨兩個人,嗌咗半隻雞及兩份飯；食得不知幾和味!!
價錢算平，但份量真係好少，一個人都要食兩份先至勉強夠飽🌝
第一次午飯時間在西灣河找吃，四圍貢時進入了太安樓，遠遠的看到長長的人龍，假定星好野，結果排了約10分鐘。味道不錯，只是份量小了點。(同枱的大媽一邊吃一邊駡：份量愈來愈小。)
位於太安樓。 海南鷄最近略貴了一點但因為實在太好吃，昨天我也吃了半隻， 約港幣89元， 值得去一試呀！
It was very delicious. When I pass this store,always there were lot's of people waited to get foods. Today I finally try chicken rice and it was awesome.
